<en-note><div><font face="Helvetica Neue"><span style="font-size: 18px;">Step1 : Install the OpenSSL using the brew </span></font></div><div><font face="Helvetica Neue"><span style="font-size: 18px;">             =&gt; <b>brew install openssl</b></span></font></div><div><font face="Helvetica Neue"><span style="font-size: 18px;"><br/></span></font></div><div><span style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; font-size: 18px;">Step 2: Download the Python source code ( such as </span><span style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; font-size: 18px;">Python-3.6.1.tgz ) and extract</span></div><div><span style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; font-size: 18px;"><br/></span></div><div><font face="Helvetica Neue"><span style="font-size: 18px;">Step 3: Change directory to the Python source folder and open the <b>Modules/Setup.dist</b>”</span></font></div><div><font face="Helvetica Neue"><span style="font-size: 18px;">             and <b>Modules/Setup</b>  files</span></font></div><div><font face="Helvetica Neue"><span style="font-size: 18px;"><br/></span></font></div><div><font face="Helvetica Neue"><span style="font-size: 18px;">Step 4. Search for “SSL” ( somewhere near line 204-209) and uncomment the lines:</span></font></div><div><span style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; font-size: 18px;">            </span><span style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;">_socket socketmodule.c</span></div><div><font face="Helvetica Neue"><span style="font-size: 18px;">             <font color="#941100"># Make sure that “SSL” is set to the OpenSSL installation directory!</font></span></font></div><div><span style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; font-size: 18px;"><b>             SSL=</b></span><span style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; font-size: 18px;"><b>/usr/local/opt/openssl</b></span></div><div><span style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; font-size: 18px;">             _ssl _ssl.c \</span></span></div><div><span style="font-weight: bold; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; font-size: 18px;">             -DUSE_SSL -I$(SSL)/include -I$(SSL)/include/openssl \</span></div><div><span style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; font-size: 18px;"/><span style="font-weight: bold; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; font-size: 18px;">             -L$(SSL)/lib -lssl -lcrypto</span></div><div><font face="Helvetica Neue"><span style="font-size: 18px;">             </span></font></div></en-note>
